---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Link from "../components/Link.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About - HUTAO667">
  <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-lg md:max-w-xl lg:max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 text-justify text-foreground animate-fade-in animate-slide-up">
    Hello, I'm HUTAO.<br><br>
    An AI application development enthusiast. I'm passionate about exploring practical applications of LLMs and enjoy the process of integrating AI capabilities into useful tools.
    <br><br>
    Currently, I'm developing UE_ToolkitAI, an AI-powered Unreal Engine toolbox that integrates multi-model LLM, Function Calling, and MCP protocol.
    <br><br>
    This blog is my technical notes organization space, documenting practical experience from AI application development to tool design.
    <br><br>
    If you're also interested in AI application development, LLM integration, or development tool design, feel free to reach out anytime.
  </div>

  <style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .animate-fade-in {
      animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    }

    .animate-slide-up {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: slideUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
